	<div itemprop="text"><p>I assume that &#8220;beast-style-switcher-css&#8221; is the ID of your link element?</p>
<p>If that&#8217;s the case, then &#8220;$switcher.href&#8221; is incorrect, I believe. You would need to do &#8220;$switcher.attr(&#8216;href&#8217;,newStyle)&#8221; instead.</p>
