	<div itemprop="text"><p>[&#8230;] Any control willing to populate the Theme Customizer must extend the WP_Customize_Control class. That class extension must be made at customize_register hook time. For major and well more detailed info see Otto on WordPress article. [&#8230;]</p>
</div>

